Rails
—————
:Rake	Run current test, spec or feature
:Rails	Interface to the rails command

:A 	Switch between source and test
:R	Switch between source and view

gf	Go to file or partial on namespace under cursor

:Eview		Open related view
:Emodel		Open related model
:Econtroller	Open related controller

:Estylesheet	Open stylesheet
:Ejavascript	Open javascript
:Elayout <tab>	Open layout
:Elocale <tab>	Open locale